Profile

Maximilian Tischer

Maximilian Tischer, born 1990 in Berlin, works in business development at Data4Life. He is also completing his doctorate in the field of entrepreneurship at RWTH Aachen University.

Maximilian Tischer studied international business administration at WHU - Otto Beisheim School of Management and ESCP Europe. Prior to that, he worked as a management consultant with the Boston Consulting Group and also has experience from various positions in the start-up and venture capital environment. Maximilian is enthusiastic about the opportunities and possibilities that digital technologies can bring to the healthcare sector.
